      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The desire to just stop the pain and be with him sounds like a desperate longing for peace, and that kind of yearning is so understandable when you're hurting this much. But that peace you're imagining isn't real; it's just the illusion of escape from this unbearable emptiness. If you're thinking about ending things, please call or text 988 immediately—there are people who want to help you through this moment.",
